      "issue": null
     },
     "reason": "RoadRunner bug (bngsim correct). RR loads init([TGF_beta_ex])=0 despite the SBML carrying initialConcentration=0.05, and no initialAssignment / rule / firing event overrides it (the only event's trigger needs stimulation_type==2, but type=1). bngsim honors the literal 0.05, so the whole TGF-beta receptor cascade activates (worst LRC_endo, relmax 1.0); RR leaves it frozen. bngsim matches the literal SBML and the biological intent."
    }
   ],
